creator: ShridLife AS
descriptionHtml:
Fitness is hard. Yet everyday, millions of people head out of their homes and down to the gym to push themselves through a workout. So, three years ago we started thinking...What if we taught biochemistry and biomechanics to a device that everyone has in their pockets? Today, we’ve done it. Introducing Abel - the digital personal trainer.

Powered by artificial intelligence, it tells you exactly how to work out in order to get fit, whether it it to run fast, lose weight or lift heavy. Abel programs your training, plans your meals and lists your groceries all within the framework of your life. With expertise in exercise and nutrition science, it’s the world’s most comprehensive fitness application.

Just tell Abel who you are and want you want to accomplish and start your training. It’s really that simple. Based on your performance, Abel optimizes the workouts to maximize your progress, so that you won’t have to take notes ever again. With Abel, you always know what exercises to do, and how to do them. But getting fit takes more than just training. Abel makes it simpler than ever to combine the food you want with the food you need. It provides thousands of dishes with simple instructions. And lets you rate what you like and replace what you don’t. It’s never been easier to train right, eat right and get the results you want.

Fitness will still be hard. But here at Abel, we believe that with the right tool everyone can reach their fitness goals. A tool that is accountable. Accessible. Adaptable.

Fitness is hard. Yet everyday, millions of people head out of their homes and down to the gym to push themselves through a workout. So, three years ago we started thinking...What if we taught biochemistry and biomechanics to a device that everyone has in their pockets? Today, we’ve done it. Introducing Abel - the digital personal trainer.

Powered by artificial intelligence, it tells you exactly how to work out in order to get fit, whether it it to run fast, lose weight or lift heavy. Abel programs your training, plans your meals and lists your groceries all within the framework of your life. With expertise in exercise and nutrition science, it’s the world’s most comprehensive fitness application.

Just tell Abel who you are and want you want to accomplish and start your training. It’s really that simple. Based on your performance, Abel optimizes the workouts to maximize your progress, so that you won’t have to take notes ever again. With Abel, you always know what exercises to do, and how to do them. But getting fit takes more than just training. Abel makes it simpler than ever to combine the food you want with the food you need. It provides thousands of dishes with simple instructions. And lets you rate what you like and replace what you don’t. It’s never been easier to train right, eat right and get the results you want.

Fitness will still be hard. But here at Abel, we believe that with the right tool everyone can reach their fitness goals. A tool that is accountable. Accessible. Adaptable.

creator: ABEL Technologies AS
descriptionHtml:
Achieving and maintaining a healthy lifestyle is hard. Everyday millions of people head out of their homes to push themselves through a workout. Still, maintaining a healthy lifestyle can be difficult. And that is precisely why we are thrilled to let you experience the solution.

Introducing Abel – a workout and nutrition app for you as a client, and an all-in-one coaching platform for you as a coach.

Are you a client?
As a client you will be assured of reaching your goals, as the app tracks your workout sessions and progression. In Abel you are connected to your coach, who gives you your workout and meal plans directly in the app. Your coach will motivate you and follow up on you – even when you are not at the gym together physically. How motivating is it, knowing that your coach is always by your side? Did you make a new record? Your coach will get a notification and celebrate your progress with you! Abel is truly the simplest app where you have everything you need to achieve your goals within health, as well as allowing you and your coach to get even closer.

Are you a coach?
As a coach you can guide your clients in achieving the lifestyle and the results they desire, as well as having everything administrative you need in one place. Really everything! With access to a database consisting of hundreds of dishes and video-explained exercises, developed by professionals, you can easily create successful programs. Want to use your own dishes or exercises? Of course! When it comes to customer contracts, payments and customer documentation, Abel takes care of it all. Having this all-in-one platform will please your everyday life with the following:
- Ensures you a total overview of your clients and your business
- Provides a significantly greater capacity to help even more customers
- A system that keeps your customers for a longer amount of time

Maintaining a healthy lifestyle will still be hard. But with Abel we believe that with the right tool and with the right coach everyone can make it work and make it last.
